    "description": "<p>When you perform a Jump, you can spend 1 AP to increase your Jump Distance for the Jump.</p><p>Make a DC 10 Acrobatics Check. </p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Your Jump Distance increases by 1. </p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Your Jump Distance increases by 2. </p></li><li><p><strong>Success (each 5):</strong> +1 Jump Distance.</p></li></ul><p><span style=\"color:rgba(44, 44, 43, 1);isolation:auto\" data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\"><em><strong>DC Tip:</strong> Remember, your Long Jump Distance equals your Jump Distance in Spaces, and your High Jump distance equals your Jump Distance in feet.</em></span></p>",
